comments: Cunningham (DET) moves slightly forward towards Markkanen (UTA) and marginal side to side contact occurs during the drive.
Duren (DET) establishes himself in Fontecchio's (UTA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Kessler (UTA) is moving alongside Bogdanovic's (DET) path and marginal contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Duren (DET) grasps Fontecchio's (UTA) right arm and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the rebound.
Kessler (UTA) goes to, not through, Bogdanovic's (DET) space as they come together at the same spot off ball.
Markkanen (UTA) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Pistons.
Sexton (UTA) cleanly dislodges the ball from Livers (DET).  The two then go to the floor in pursuit of the loose ball, and the contact is incidental.
Sexton (UTA) does not intentionally kick the ball away from Livers (DET) as he attempts to secure the loose ball.
Utah is granted a timeout when Sexton (UTA) recovers the ball and pins it against his side.
Markkanen (UTA) is moving alongside Bogdanovic's (DET) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Kessler (UTA) legally contests Bogdanovic's (DET) driving shot attempt.
Duren (DET) makes contact with the ball, and with the part of Kessler's (UTA) hand that is on the ball.
Kessler (UTA) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Pistons.
Burks (DET) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Kessler (UTA) cleanly blocks Livers' (DET) jump shot attempt.
Livers (DET) is already in Markkanen's (UTA) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Markkanen (UTA) brings his hands toward Hayes (DET) and marginal contact occurs as Markkanen releases away to pop.
Sexton (UTA) is moving alongside Burks' (DET) path and marginal contact occurs as they come together at the same spot.
Sexton (UTA) avoids making contact with Burks' (DET) arm as he defends the jump shot attempt.
Markkanen (UTA) is firming up in Burks' (DET) path and marginal contact occurs as Burks commits to going under the pick.
Duren (DET) is already in Markkanen's (UTA) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Cunningham (DET) legally contests Clarkson's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Fontecchio (UTA) makes clean contact with the ball as Bogdanovic (DET) attempts to pass the ball.  Bogdanovic then legally regains possession.
Kessler (UTA) initiates contact with Bogdanovic's (DET) arm, which affects his shot attempt near the basket.
Fontecchio (UTA) is bracing for the contact from Cunningham (DET), and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Markkanen (UTA) makes clean contact with the ball as Burks (DET) attempts to pass the ball.
Markkanen (UTA) lowers his hand and makes contact with Burks' (DET) arm, affecting his shot near the rim.
Bogdanovic (DET) commits a take foul on Clarkson (UTA).
Burks (DET) commits a take foul on Clarkson (UTA).
Sexton (UTA) extends his right hand and initiates contact with Burks (DET) prior to the start of his upward shooting motion.
Livers (DET) cleanly ties up Markkanen (UTA) and a jump ball is correctly called.
Ivey (DET) cleanly deflects the ball away from Sexton (UTA) as they pursue the loose ball.
Cunningham (DET) cleanly ties up Collins (UTA) and a jump ball is correctly called.
Duren (DET) steps forward into Markkanen's (UTA) path and delivers contact with his hip/side during the pick.
Clarkson (UTA) absorbs the marginal contact initiated by Cunningham (DET) as he contests the jump shot attempt.

Hayes (DET) extends his arm forward into Sexton's (UTA) path and impedes his FOM.  After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined the foul occurred prior to the ball being released, and an away from the play foul was assessed.
Hayes (DET) commits a take foul on Sexton (UTA).
